<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal David suon Aksi vak hawihtak chun,
 Bethlehem A salh vaka;
 Vakna thu chu puongin a gen viel ui,
 &quot;Chungnung penah lopi pen hen&quot; a tiu.

[V2]
 &quot;Chungnung penah lopi pen hen!&quot; ti'n la asau,(2)
 Zailan awi ui, van Angel mipiten;
 &quot;Chamna thu leng hen&quot;ti'n zaila a sau.

[V3]
 2. Belampute'n belam a ven lai un,
 Lal sawlchak lopi tak chun;
 &quot;Bethlehema Hukdampa hung pieng chu,
 A kiengah va chieh un&quot; ti'n a hilh hi.

[V4]
 3. Thangvan mipite khu galin dawn diu,
 Lal Krista a khen niu chun,
 Nuoi simlei hi ding in gal thil ui.
 &quot;Chungnung penah lopi pen hen&quot; a tiu.</lyrics>
<title>Chungnung Penah Lopi Hen!</title>
</song>